to our communities in Te Tairawhiti.

3514
03:25:37.550 --> 03:25:41.350
Before we speak to the legislation itself, it's important to acknowledge that our

3515
03:25:41.370 --> 03:25:44.270
region has a long history with this kaupapa.

3516
03:25:44.280 --> 03:25:48.090
More than 100 years ago, Sir Apirana Ngata with the East Coast Maori

3517
