sexual violence.

3592
03:29:59.914 --> 03:30:03.354
We work upstream, strength based, across a broad range of areas.

3593
03:30:04.474 --> 03:30:07.934
But when we look at the huge harm in our communities and whanau from family and

3594
03:30:08.014 --> 03:30:11.234
sexual violence, alcohol is a key contributing factor.

3595
03:30:12.654 --> 03:30:16.354
We know all too well the impact that policy, good or bad, has in our communities.

3596
03:30:17.614 --> 03:30:21.554
One of the things that concerns us about this bill is that it arrives in a

3597
03:30:21.594 --> 03:30:25.214
region that is already carrying a significant burden of alcohol related harm.

3598
03:30:26.634 --> 03:30:29.974
In Tairawhiti, we continue to experience some of the highest rates of hazardous

3599
03:30:30.034 --> 03:30:31.014
drinking in the country.

3600
03:30:32.214 --> 03:30:35.994
We continue to see alcohol featuring prominently in family harm incidents.

3601
03:30:36.414 --> 03:30:39.023
We continue to see the impacts on whanau wellbeing.

3602
03:30:40.734 --> 03:30:44.074
When you've spent years attending those incidents, it becomes difficult to support

3603
03:30:44.083 --> 03:30:47.224
