3612
03:31:10.184 --> 03:31:12.654
And that point speaks to our biggest concern with the bill.

3613
03:31:13.134 --> 03:31:16.914
New Zealand has not had a national alcohol strategy for more than 20 years.

3614
03:31:17.814 --> 03:31:21.714
During that time, we've continued to amend legislation, respond to

3615
03:31:21.754 --> 03:31:25.294
emerging issues, and invest in different initiatives, but we've done so

3616
03:31:25.374 --> 03:31:28.454
without a clear national framework that brings those efforts together.

3617
03:31:29.074 --> 03:31:32.714
As a result, we're often debating individual policy changes without first

3618
03:31:32.874 --> 03:31:34.294
asking what success looks like.

3619
03:31:35.214 --> 03:31:38.974
While national data shows many young people are drinking less, those

3620
