3622
03:31:46.114 --> 03:31:47.514
What are we trying to achieve?

3623
03:31:48.694 --> 03:31:52.094
What does a healthier alcohol environment look like for all our

3624
03:31:52.134 --> 03:31:55.814
communities? How do we reduce harm while supporting community

3625
03:31:55.894 --> 03:31:59.484
wellbeing? How do we meet our obligations under Te Tiriti o

3626
03:31:59.484 --> 03:32:03.374
Waitangi? Those are strategic questions,

3627
03:32:03.494 --> 03:32:06.314
and we believe they deserve strategic answers.

3628
03:32:06.374 --> 03:32:10.214
That is why one of our strongest recommendations is that this bill be paused while

3629
03:32:10.234 --> 03:32:14.054
