3630
03:32:14.094 --> 03:32:17.924
informed, Te Tiriti led, and aligned with international

3631
03:32:18.034 --> 03:32:18.994
best practice.

3632
03:32:20.574 --> 03:32:21.954
All right. Thank you, guys.

