3643
03:32:51.194 --> 03:32:54.534
ways we can turn our commitment to the wellbeing of future generations.

3644
03:32:55.354 --> 03:32:59.334
The reason both Jeremy and I are here today is because alcohol contributes so

3645
03:32:59.374 --> 03:33:03.294
