3646
03:33:04.074 --> 03:33:07.084
Jeremy has seen it through decades of observing, reporting on the life of our

3647
03:33:07.114 --> 03:33:10.954
community. I've seen it through 25 years responding to the consequences when

3648
03:33:10.994 --> 03:33:11.694
things go wrong.

3649
03:33:12.934 --> 03:33:16.694
Both experiences have led us to Hikitea Tane Ora and lead us to the same

3650
