3651
03:33:19.914 --> 03:33:23.114
Communities have solutions. Prevention does work.

3652
03:33:23.934 --> 03:33:26.414
Strong policies matter, and community voice matters.

3653
03:33:27.094 --> 03:33:30.974
We respectfully ask the committee to protect that voice, strengthen rather than

3654
